01:06:04.480 --> 01:06:06.003
I'll be fine.
I just--

01:06:06.120 --> 01:06:08.646
I just need to work.

01:06:13.600 --> 01:06:14.969
Hey.
Hi.

01:06:15.080 --> 01:06:18.163
Marcus' fish died last night.

01:06:18.280 --> 01:06:19.406
