01:06:19.520 --> 01:06:24.447
He thinks Luis had something
to do with it.

01:06:24.560 --> 01:06:26.483
Did he?

01:06:32.560 --> 01:06:36.406
Tell me you didn't do something
to Marcus' fish.

01:06:36.520 --> 01:06:37.968
What?
Luis, tell me.

01:06:38.080 --> 01:06:40.845
